    "en": {
      "title": "Work stoppage for 48 hours",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Today (23) Railway Station Principals Association has announced that they will withdraw from the work of issuing tickets from 6 pm to 48 hours.",
        "The Railway Department had announced that the revised train fare will come into effect from today (23).",
        "However, it is to be noted that Railway Station Master's Association has informed that there are discrepancies in the revised fares and they have taken steps to distribute tickets at the old prices."
      ],
